<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Coverlet on Life Deletion Guide</title><link>https://liguobao.github.io/tags/coverlet/</link><description>Recent content in Coverlet on Life Deletion Guide</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2019 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://liguobao.github.io/tags/coverlet/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>.NET Core Unit Test Coverage with coverlet + ReportGenerator</title><link>https://liguobao.github.io/p/.net-core-unit-test-coverage-with-coverlet--reportgenerator/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Apr 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://liguobao.github.io/p/.net-core-unit-test-coverage-with-coverlet--reportgenerator/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="test-coverage-with-coverlet--reportgenerator"&gt;Test Coverage with coverlet + ReportGenerator
&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;Need coverage for .NET Core? Use coverlet to collect, and ReportGenerator to render HTML.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="coverlet"&gt;coverlet
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Install either as a global tool or as an MSBuild package:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;dotnet tool install --global coverlet.console
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;or add to your test project:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-xml" data-lang="xml"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;&amp;lt;PackageReference&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Include=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;coverlet.msbuild&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="na"&gt;Version=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;#34;2.5.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="nt"&gt;/&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Then run tests with coverage:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;3
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;4
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;dotnet &lt;span class="nb"&gt;test&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; /p:CollectCoverage&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nb"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; /p:CoverletOutput&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s1"&gt;&amp;#39;./results/&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="se"&gt;\
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; /p:CoverletOutputFormat&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;opencover
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Outputs &lt;code&gt;coverage.opencover.xml&lt;/code&gt; under &lt;code&gt;results/&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="reportgenerator"&gt;ReportGenerator
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Render humanâ€‘readable reports from XML:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;div class="chroma"&gt;
&lt;table class="lntable"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lnt"&gt;2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class="lntd"&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"&gt;&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh"&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;dotnet tool install --global dotnet-reportgenerator-globaltool
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt;reportgenerator &lt;span class="s1"&gt;&amp;#39;-reports:UnitTests/results/*.xml&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s1"&gt;&amp;#39;-targetdir:UnitTests/results&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Open &lt;code&gt;UnitTests/results/index.htm&lt;/code&gt; to view the coverage report.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>